<strong>2. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 9<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0 duy v\u00e0 l\u00e0m b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp cho h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0R\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh\u00a0h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c l\u00ed thuy\u1ebft theo c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh..<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0m b\u00e0i theo nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u01b0 duy cho c\u00e1c em.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd gi\u1eefa \u00f4n b\u00e0i c\u0169 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p b\u00e0i m\u1edbi, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh \u201ch\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u ch\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5y\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gi\u00e1o \u00e1n, ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i theo ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1, chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 t\u1eeb d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0R\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m b\u00e0i th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng b\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p trong \u0111\u1ec1 thi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u0103m h\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">\u2666\u00a0G\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh sai s\u00f3t trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m b\u00e0i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-875\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su-toan-lop-9-luyen-thi-vao-lop-10-300x117.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su-toan-lop-9-luyen-thi-vao-lop-10-300x117.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su-toan-lop-9-luyen-thi-vao-lop-10-768x300.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su-toan-lop-9-luyen-thi-vao-lop-10-1024x400.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/gia-su-toan-lop-9-luyen-thi-vao-lop-10.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: B\u00ed k\u00edp h\u1ecdc <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top1-gia-su-van-ha-noi-bang-gia-mon-van-moi-nhat-2018\/\"><strong>gia s\u01b0 V\u0103n gi\u1ecfi<\/strong><\/a> m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i cha m\u1eb9 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 con h\u1ecdc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, xem ngay: T\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z, c\u1ea9m nang <strong>&#8220;<a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/\">gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<\/a>&#8220;<\/strong> gi\u1ecfi, gi\u00fap con l\u00e0m to\u00e1n t\u01b0 duy t\u1ed1t, v\u0103n hay, ch\u1eef \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Bang_gia_gia_su_day_Toan_lop_9\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>3. B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 9<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><em style=\"font-size: 100%;\">\n<table id=\"tablepress-15\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-15\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u0110\u1ed0I T\u01af\u1ee2NG<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">130.000 \u2013 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000 - 280.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">160.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">3 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-15 from cache -->\n&gt;&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i, h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tu\u1ef3 theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 hotline: <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">096.31.38.511<\/span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/em><i>\u00a0<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 gia s\u01b0<\/strong><\/a> c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn ngay 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Khac_biet_khi_hoc_gia_su_tai_nha\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>4. Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t khi h\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc th\u00eam th\u1ea7y c\u00f4, trung t\u00e2m luy\u1ec7n thi<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>+ \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; B\u00e1m s\u00e1t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean l\u1edbp.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00e9 ti\u1ebfp thu t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>+ Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc th\u00eam truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng 1 th\u1ea7y, nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp. B\u00e9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m v\u00e0i ch\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc sinh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng li\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng cao, V\u00ec:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; H\u1ecdc sinh ham ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n b\u00e8<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec3u so\u00e1t t\u1eeb ph\u1ee5 huynh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c s\u00e1t sao trong ki\u1ec3m tra b\u00e0i v\u1edf<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_878\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-878\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-878\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/uu-nhuoc-diem-cua-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-300x189.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/uu-nhuoc-diem-cua-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-300x189.jpg 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/uu-nhuoc-diem-cua-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha-768x484.jpg 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/uu-nhuoc-diem-cua-hoc-gia-su-tai-nha.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-878\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><em>\u01afu nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n l\u1edbp 9<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc luy\u1ec7n thi gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>+ \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; H\u1ecdc gia s\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn t\u00e2m trong h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; H\u1ecdc k\u00e8m 1 &#8211; 1, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u ch\u1ed7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u ngay ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7m tay ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a con<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m tra b\u00e0i v\u1edf, k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi gian, c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c di chuy\u1ec3n, \u0111i l\u1ea1i. Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>+ Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean l\u1edbp nh\u01b0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m c\u00f2n \u00edt.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Quyen_loi_khi_den_voi_trung_tam\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><strong>5. Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 to\u00e1n l\u1edbp 9 theo \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed n\u1ebfu gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn gia s\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; \u0110\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o khi gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e1t sinh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-879\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-binh-minh-300x100.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-binh-minh-300x100.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-binh-minh-768x256.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-binh-minh-1024x342.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/quyen-loi-khi-den-voi-trung-tam-binh-minh.png 1349w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%; color: #000000;\"><i>\u00a0&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#